[ ENGLISH]
With_Made_In_House bringing you some of the hottest , boutique events this year we are excited to announce our largest event yet .
We are proud to officially announce the worlds current bust duo straight from Sweden_Axwell / \ Ingrosso , perfroming their world famous “ Sun_Is_Shining_Tour ” to be performed at the Long_Island_Castle this December 10th .
The event will be the first ever hosted inside the famous “ Church_Compound ” creating the most unique event ever in Vietnam .
Featuring some of the best upcoming international talent , spread over the famous outdoor Tropical_Stage and Church_Compound . MIH will only be supplying a capacity amount of * * * 2,500 * * * tickets , making it the closest you may ever get to see Axwell_Ingrosso perform .
Spread over 8hrs , 2 stages , and 7 artist ' s , Made_In_House will produce the most intimate , unforgetable event for 2015
